item.description: Back by popular demand we are going to meet at the beach again for some great volleyball.  This meetup location is subject to change depending on how clean the beach is, however I prefer this location. Parking should be easy to find this time of year. I will try to be there by 2:30pm to put up the net. Anyone that can help please let me know. Otherwise we will start at 3pm. This meetup will be cancelled if there are not at least 8 people signed up by the Saturday before or the weather is bad. Negative behavior is not permitted. We should all help putting up the net if we are available. We should all be having fun! Please everyone that can help putting up the net it would be much appreciated.  It would also be great if a couple people could bring a rake. If you are new to this we would love you to join.  Let's hope the weather is nice and sunny! New people are always welcome and don't hesitate to email me with questions. After we go out for drinks at a local bar.
item.how_to_find_us: We will be there setting up the volleyball net! Let us know you are there and we will welcome you!
